Aside from the program included, grep can be used to search for a repeating key like so:

dd if=/dev/zero of=./zerofile bs=1M count=4
./yaxafileutil -e ./zerofile ./zerofile.keystream
./stripsalt ./zerofile.keystream ./zerofile.keystream.stripped 24
hd -v ./zerofile.keystream.stripped > ./zerofile.keystream.hex
grep -n "$(head -n 1 ./zerofile.keystream.hex | cut -d " " -f 2-10)" ./zerofile.keystream.hex

Which will output something like this:

1:00000000  35 79 b8 ce cb 2e 9e de  37 aa 9d e9 62 9e 34 31  |5y......7...b.41|
213201:00340d00  35 79 b8 ce cb 2e 9e de  37 aa 9d e9 62 9e 34 31  |5y......7...b.41|

grep prints the line number in the hex dump that the first 8 bytes repeat at. 213201 ( minus one ) * 16 bytes = 3411200

So if the keystream is kept under 3411200 bytes the key will be non-periodic

dd if=/dev/zero of=./zerofile bs=1M count=3
./yaxafileutil -e ./zerofile ./zerofile.keystream
./stripsalt ./zerofile.keystream ./zerofile.keystream.stripped 24
hd -v ./zerofile.keystream.stripped > ./zerofile.keystream.hex
grep -n "$(head -n 1 ./zerofile.keystream.hex | cut -d " " -f 2-10)" ./zerofile.keystream.hex

grep will only show one line matching:
1:00000000  7f be 99 1c b7 18 bb d8  82 81 32 29 28 92 16 21  |..........2)(..!|

As long as the password file is kept under 3411200 bytes the keystream will be non-periodic.

The periodsearch.c program will provide this functionality without the need to strip the salt.

dd if=/dev/zero of=./zerofile bs=1M count=4
./yaxafileutil -e ./zerofile ./zerofile.keystream
./periodsearch ./zerofile.keystream 8

Searching for: d54cf92c977f6481
Searching for: 82639aa255a1a83
Searching for: e0c873456e163ceb
Searching for: 3c2e948185b19320
Periodic key begins at file offset 24 and ends at file offset 3411224
Key period is 3411200 bytes

vs

dd if=/dev/zero of=./zerofile bs=1M count=3
./yaxafileutil -e ./zerofile ./zerofile.keystream
./periodsearch ./zerofile.keystream 8

Searching for: bc3f3a72bcb09697
Searching for: 871f787279b44db
Searching for: 6f716658c5923b4
Searching for: 1759719bf633e9e
Searching for: c6b15282292f4fe5
Searching for: b0c58d974fdd9
Searching for: 42104056efa52132
Searching for: 71fdff527a6c2a
Searching for: bb80ee2dddc9062
Searching for: ac7abc56ef43a89
Searching for: c9459d4b679465c
(Searching will continue until it fines a matching byte sequence 8 bytes long as specified)
